1
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:38,170
¡Nami-swan!

2
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,410
¡Sí!

3
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,380
Mola

4
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,380
Shi

5
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,380
Chibukai

6
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,380
Fansub!

7
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:19,380
Sierra circular.

8
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:12,380
¡Faltan diez minutos!

9
00:10:16,350 --> 00:10:20,770
Este es el verdadero
 tiempo límite.

10
00:10:20,770 --> 00:10:22,480
¡El destino de este país...

11
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:25,150
...se decidirá...

12
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,940
...en diez minutos!

13
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,720
Mola

14
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,720
Shi

15
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,720
Chibukai

16
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,720
Fansub!

17
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,720
Octavo guerrero del mar bajo el rey.

18
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:11,380
Mola

19
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:11,380
Shi

20
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:11,380
Chibukai

21
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:11,380
Fansub!

22
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:11,380
Escopeta.

23
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:39,880
Mola

24
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:39,880
Shi

25
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:39,880
Chibukai

26
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:39,880
Fansub!

27
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:39,880
Luffy de agua.

28
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:45,680
¿Este mocoso va en serio?

29
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:58,280
¿Acaso no comprende la situación?

30
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,010
¡Maldición!

31
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:29,350
¡Mi cuerpo...!

32
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:35,720
Mola

33
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:35,720
Shi

34
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:35,720
